  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/7e0d5ed6ec032eebb8843b50f80fea01.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/8f56ca392c2bacf9ea816b41cd791d0a.poster.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/8f56ca392c2bacf9ea816b41cd791d0a.webm?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/8f56ca392c2bacf9ea816b41cd791d0a.mp4?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/17900b8911328fb57074899c22a002a5.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Randoville is a medieval city-builder but with <strong>nuance</strong>.<br>Your every move will be controlled by <strong>D20</strong> Cube!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Appearance of buildings<br></li><li>Quality of resource points<br></li><li>Number of extracted resources<br></li><li>Results of events</li></ul>Will be decided by throwing a D20!<br>But don't be frustrated, it is possible to improve your <strong>luck</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/1a9e361cbd8f81a8a08ae9c13b29f4c6.poster.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/1a9e361cbd8f81a8a08ae9c13b29f4c6.webm?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/1a9e361cbd8f81a8a08ae9c13b29f4c6.mp4?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/13b4eb0d53bd2bf6127ee7721fff2a0e.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Choose what to build, roll the <strong>Dice</strong> and get the result!<br>The better the <strong>number</strong>, the easier it will be for you. <br>Build, earn, <strong>level up</strong> and open new.<br>Once you are stuck, give up on everything and <strong>REGRESS</strong>!<br>There is no limit to perfection, so you can start again as many times as you want, and small and tireless cuboys will help you to reach the peak!<br>Try not to harm them with your huge Dice!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/7c83592b337e47aef1a1d4d6fe782ceb.poster.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/7c83592b337e47aef1a1d4d6fe782ceb.webm?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/7c83592b337e47aef1a1d4d6fe782ceb.mp4?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/6b6c765efabac995143bd437b3caa48a.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>If you are tired of being medieval architect, try yourself in <strong>fishing</strong>, or... i don't know, <strong>Mine Kart Racing League</strong>? Small minigames will let you take your mind off and earn some useful things for your village.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/a243caf38dd9a33568a9353e90773300.poster.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/a243caf38dd9a33568a9353e90773300.webm?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/a243caf38dd9a33568a9353e90773300.mp4?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
